Summary

Dataset: Bangladesh

Measure: Emergent Numeracy at Midline (size1 - puzzle)

Comparison variable: Gender (0, 1)

Items with no variance: none

Items with no variance within levels of comparison variable: b puzzle

Bias detection method: IRT

Total number of biased items: 9 out of 28

Type of item bias: non-uniform

b Items were not included in the IRT-based DIF analysis and were not used to compute IRT-based treatment effects.
